  10 Oct 2009; Tristan Heaven <nyhm@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r3.ebuild:
  EAPI=2; remove dedicated and opengl USE flags; let games-mods.eclass
  handle install

  28 Jul 2008; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing myself from metadata.xml since I am retiring from the project.

  10 Jan 2007; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2.ebuild, ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r3.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64/x86 and removing older versions.

*ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r3 (07 Nov 2006)

  07 Nov 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  +ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r3.ebuild:
  Added new revision for testing which uses the brand-spankin-new
  games-mods.eclass to reduce ebuild code.

  26 Sep 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2.ebuild:
  Remove dependency on ut2004 since this causes circular dependencies. Closing
  bug #149024.

  14 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2.ebuild:
  Fixed unpacking and closing bug #129883.

  13 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild:
  Removing older ebuilds so I don't mistakenly remove the wrong one again.

  13 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2.ebuild:
  Marking stable on amd64 and x86 to keep users from having to downgrade to an
  older version of the ebuild.

*ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2 (13 Apr 2006)

  13 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  -ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1.ebuild, +ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r2.ebuild:
  I have forced a revision bump here since this package will now *always*
  install the ECE content. I'm sure some users are going to hate me for this,
  but it had to be done. Closing bug #97726.

  11 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1.ebuild:
  Marking stable on amd64/x86 to bring in new Mega bonuspack and to close bug
  #129373.

  31 Mar 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild, ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1.ebuild:
  Changed nomirror to mirror and nostrip to strip.

  24 Mar 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild, ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1.ebuild:
  Removed unnecessary pkg_postinst.

*ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1 (14 Mar 2006)

  14 Mar 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild, +ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1-r1.ebuild:
  Added new ebuild using the megapack distfile. Ebuild by Paul Bredbury
  <brebs@sent.com>. Closing bug #116334.

  30 Aug 2005; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild:
  Changed to match new 3dgamers mirrors structure in thirdpartymirrors.

  16 May 2005; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1.ebuild:
  Marking stable on x86/amd64.

*ut2004-bonuspack-ece-1 (22 Feb 2005)

